{"tid":1204483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察，你哋班撚樣係賣港賊","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T16:36:10.000Z","uid":26332,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"936f451f8ce08f06b438e2a7b539d93df8876259","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全香港警察聽住<br />\n保護市民係你哋天職<br />\n無保護不特止，仲要傷害市民，與民為敵？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，有ORDER叫你向市民開槍，見一個殺一個，你會開槍，定違抗命令保護我哋？<br />\n<br />\n如果你選擇聽ORDER開槍<br />\n你地班仆街撚樣死黑警<br />\n你地係<ins>賣港賊</ins>！<br />\n</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"8aab12649a1fb318263387733908067918fdc8ad","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察，賣港賊</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"aa24e7a9e6880be9393edf5b81f685be41042c49","tid":1204483,"uid":258285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:20:29.000Z","msg":"5.如何辨認警務人員之身份/警察委任證之真偽？<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。 如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署 查詢。"},{"pid":"27e84985057a4d55a9c51a8822fbbb7592392891","tid":1204483,"uid":255494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9343337e71f2636d6cf26fca1e942f8123452e92","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港警察，賣港賊<br />\n</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d38db9efcf9e01380f02439650b571663f8ce902","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港警察，賣港賊</div></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"448d6c5bc0c1b34a8d942386d837e7fd233ac9b2","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港警察，賣港賊</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1f24a10c07c019fa958160cccc53755686c1f16d","tid":1204483,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港警察，賣港賊</div></strong></span></span>"}]}